{"tid":485651,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"願可為你 細味每分袋泥","createTime":"2017-12-01T06:26:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-07T05:06:53.000Z","uid":102814,"like":74,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"7990427575012e44c56359403412566294309aac","tid":485651,"uid":102814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T06:26:51.000Z","msg":"你 見面最講實際<br />\n互摸褲浪 攻擊勢不可擋<br />\n我願意留低　烏身去墊底<br />\n甚至KY也已備滿花蕾<br />\n<br />\n我　會為你躺下去<br />\n自摸誘惑　方使你扯得起<br />\n再為你含撚　緩慢的吞吐<br />\n甚至勾起我愛慾來全面進攻<br />\n<br />\n願可為你　細味每分袋泥<br />\n從春袋裏　吻下這一啖最矜貴<br />\n是否願意　愛著那胯下泥<br />\n來伸脷到　最盡去瀨  唯怕袋太污穢<br />\n<br />\n我　暗地裡親下去<br />\n濃郁氣味　剛好帶點酸宿<br />\n眼淚也狂標　瞬間想咳血<br />\n但怕今晚無慰藉無懼被臭冤<br />\n<br />\n願可為你　細味每分袋泥<br />\n從春袋裏　吻下這一啖最矜貴<br />\n是否願意　愛著那胯下泥<br />\n來伸脷到　最盡去瀨  唯怕袋太污穢<br />\n<br />\n越講越餲　正是這種袋泥<br />\n流芳萬里    鑽入肺泡無處可抖<br />\n最終病發    愛慾已經盡忘<br />\n逃生未晚    我願你春袋爆裂也不計<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"534111977c57738a60ba81bd46689c97035ae4d6","tid":485651,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T06:48:10.000Z","msg":"推到有gay巴唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d1a2abeaa60ff013f54d768435c73317e89b8b9","tid":485651,"uid":2534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T07:08:16.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c8611c33976a8e300acb198aa07b24daa7e385d","tid":485651,"uid":48441,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T07:08:45.000Z","msg":"係咪